description.narrative: End-line studies on quality early childhood education models in Kupang and Bogor districts were completed, which demonstrated improvements in learning process/environment as well as children’s developmental outcomes compared to the baseline. At national level a technical guideline for the implementation of the Holistic and Integrated ECD National Action Plan was developed and waiting for the promulgation by the Coordinating Ministry for Human Development and Culture. In collaboration with the Central Bureau of Statistics, SDG4 monitoring advanced including the analysis of young children’s developmental outcomes as well as the initiation of the development of a new Early Childhood Development Index module.; | Status:Met | As-of Date:01/12/2020
